name: Delivery Schedule Details
query:
select
 date as "Date:Date:85",
 delivery_note_no as "Delivery Note No:Data:120",
 customer_ref as "Customer Ref:Link/Customer:120",
 lorry_no as "Lorry No:Link/Carrier:120",
 driver as "Driver:Driver:120",
 trip as "Trip:Data:90",
 contact_person_name as "Contact Person:Data:130",
 mobile_no as "Mobile No:Data:120",
 remarks as "Remarks:Data:120",
 name as "Delivery Schedule:Link/Delivery Schedule:120"
FROM
 `tabDelivery Schedule` order by modified desc;
